{"tid":1536987,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"今日見到個藍絲靚post，有曬陣營，少數暴力黃絲今次仲唔收皮","createTime":"2019-09-03T18:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T19:25:28.000Z","uid":280192,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"95671e69f04702da18ca030ef9c8deaa9b825bd1","tid":1536987,"uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:39:20.000Z","msg":"細節已經忘記左，原post更精闢，但我已找不到。以下係憑發夢記憶寫的，好擔心黃絲會用來救暴徒。<br />\n<br />\n簡單來講，以下幾個step，係教藍絲對付暴徒的方法：<br />\n<br />\n1.當遇到暴徒破壞，或欺壓善良市民，咁藍絲就一齊排陣叫口號，如&ldquo;保衛市民&rdquo;。 (呢點係為左確認附近溫和派的同路人)<br />\n<br />\n2.當叫的人數累積夠多，就一起舉三指手勢繼續叫口號。(舉手勢係為左確認肯暫時化身勇武的同路人。當然肯出手先好舉，勇敢的可第一個舉，否則就等夠人先)<br />\n<br />\n3. 叫到咁上下，當舉手勢人數夠多，亦即表示在場肯集體行動的人夠多。<br />\n<br />\n4. 心跳時刻，一面舉一面叫，準備各種物資係手，前後左右望望對方眼神有無愛意，有feel就集體行動。雷霆一擊成功就散，中出即飛。<br />\n<br />\n5. 如果人數真係唔夠，也只好專心影相和撤退。<br />\n<br />\n見過無數次直播，幾個冒警就可以撲低一個年輕人，任由他痛苦被捕，流血被打，現場其他人明明有十倍市民，想衝又唔知點做，因為無整齊節奏，只有自己一個衝，只會送頭。<br />\n<br />\n所以話黃絲廢，有腦藍絲就諗到好方法。但吊詭的是藍絲本身用不到，因為最重要係人數夠多。<br />\n<br />\n記住，呢個方法只可以用來保護善良市民，制服暴徒的。衝擊真警察放犯的行為，係絕對唔應該做架。"},{"pid":"25f93a36980ec9fa737e7e62bffeb16c9a8271b2","tid":1536987,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:39:30.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bfde117f3c7769a6df046c9fc8cd446e531e1114","tid":1536987,"uid":5264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:40:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">「我正式宣佈9月4號起，<br />\n抗爭行動需要升級！<br />\n勇武要對準高官！」</div></strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1536874/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1536874/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">孫子兵法，<br />\n<br />\n求其上，<br />\n得其中，<br />\n<br />\n求其中，<br />\n得其下，<br />\n<br />\n求其下，<br />\n必敗。</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f7f4d1978628a13659f03e26c57f467be31297c7","tid":1536987,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:41:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHcuNJL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHcuNJL.jpg&h=417a49e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不反對通知書申請中<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n9月6日 反濫捕 抗威權集會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535223</a>"},{"pid":"17fee59cc3f6fa9d764d9da4aa2a94fa39368499","tid":1536987,"uid":311198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:41:22.0